<p><strong>Frequently Asked Questions – Coronavirus (COVID-19)</strong></p>

<ul>
<li><a href="#Confirmed%20Case">What will happen if the District faces a confirmed case?</a></li>
	<li><a href="#Make%20Up">If school is required to close, will the missed days have to be made up?</a></li>
