	<li><a href="#Field%20Trips">Will school field trips run as long as school remains open?</a></li>
	<li><a href="#Absences">Can I choose to keep my child home from school even if school is open?</a></li>
	<li><a href="#Lunch">Will the school still provide meals for free/reduced lunch children?</a></li>
	<li><a href="#What%20is%20Corona">What is coronavirus?</a></li>
	<li><a href="#Symptoms">What are the common symptoms?</a></li>
